    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies for exceptional throttle response. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis has been maintained with a focus on mechanical integrity, including proactive subframe reinforcement and a serviced dual-VANOS system to ensure optimal valve timing. Suspended by a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup, the handling remains sharp and predictable. Ventilated compound rotors provide consistent thermal management under load. A mechanically sound icon ready for spirited canyon runs.",
